WEBVTT

00:00.300 --> 00:02.484
Previously on "Salem"...

00:04.868 --> 00:06.212
Black Sunday is coming.

00:06.243 --> 00:08.328
We have but five days
left of life in Salem.

00:08.383 --> 00:11.125
We must move inside the mansion.
The only safe place is inside.

00:11.160 --> 00:13.189
There's one with child.
Will you have a look?

00:13.244 --> 00:14.304
With child?

00:14.650 --> 00:16.971
- What's your name?
- Gloriana.

00:17.147 --> 00:18.711
- You're the baby's father?
- Mm-hmm.

00:19.017 --> 00:20.732
Cotton Mather.

00:21.451 --> 00:23.553
Wha...

00:23.554 --> 00:27.588
I have ensured your child
a healthy, happy life

00:27.614 --> 00:30.578
as the beloved child of
Cotton Mather and his wife,

00:30.592 --> 00:31.750
Anne Hale.

00:35.422 --> 00:37.046
Isaac is a truth teller!

00:37.243 --> 00:41.241
Three cheers for Isaac!

00:41.478 --> 00:43.570
- Ugh!
- You freed us, Isaac.

00:45.823 --> 00:48.148
We're your men now.

00:48.573 --> 00:49.628
I have a surprise for you.

00:50.315 --> 00:53.322
Black Sunday will be
a new beginning for us.

00:54.714 --> 00:56.701
Our brothers must be released.

00:56.713 --> 00:59.666
While you play with
toys, they burn in hell.

00:59.691 --> 01:00.930
Perhaps I made a mistake

01:00.955 --> 01:02.745
choosing you of all of them to help me.

01:02.776 --> 01:05.102
The devil's brother will destroy Mary

01:05.104 --> 01:06.775
unless you destroy him first.

01:06.812 --> 01:09.822
You must forge a dagger with that in it

01:09.878 --> 01:12.106
and kill him with the dagger.

01:12.128 --> 01:15.046
We must find out what Sebastian knows.

01:15.058 --> 01:16.698
If you have no magic, either,

01:16.737 --> 01:18.524
how can you expect to stop Sebastian?

01:20.003 --> 01:21.820
Alden is my past. You...

01:21.826 --> 01:24.004
- are my future.
- I believe that, Mary.

01:24.558 --> 01:26.650
I may not be able to
change in an instant

01:26.675 --> 01:28.127
the way you feel about him,

01:28.378 --> 01:30.967
but I can change the
way he feels about you.

01:37.433 --> 01:39.783
- No kiss goodnight?
- I hate you.

01:40.823 --> 01:42.110
You cannot deny it was good.

01:42.143 --> 01:44.589
And that is precisely why I hate you.

01:50.737 --> 01:52.422
If that is what your hatred tastes like,

01:52.441 --> 01:53.898
I look forward to your love.

01:54.018 --> 01:55.362
Oh, do they make love in hell?

01:55.731 --> 01:57.753
Because surely as the
sun is near rising,

01:57.778 --> 01:59.719
the boy will see you
there before he lets me go.

01:59.723 --> 02:02.827
I told you I can free
us of him, and I will.

02:04.839 --> 02:07.862
Leave with me before
Sunday's blood dawn.

02:08.601 --> 02:10.496
My family castle lies
far across the ocean,

02:10.514 --> 02:12.361
and I can take us there.

02:16.190 --> 02:19.180
Stop tempting me.

02:19.581 --> 02:20.813
It is no use.

02:20.831 --> 02:24.083
- Even if I wanted to, I cannot.
- Yes, you can.

02:24.690 --> 02:26.041
Let Salem burn.

02:26.079 --> 02:29.263
Let the boy rant over
his charred puppets.

02:29.284 --> 02:31.854
You owe nothing, and
you leave nothing behind.

02:32.034 --> 02:34.813
You've never even seen the world
outside these muddy borders.

02:35.276 --> 02:37.134
The old world is filled with splendors.

02:37.151 --> 02:40.319
This new world is a cesspool...
and Salem its rank bottom.

02:40.581 --> 02:42.289
You do not understand.

02:42.331 --> 02:45.443
The Essex used their sacred
tree to resurrect my life force.

02:45.480 --> 02:46.851
I am forever bound to it.

02:46.882 --> 02:49.529
They warned me I can never
travel beyond its roots.

02:49.714 --> 02:52.157
And you believe those
shriveled tree worshippers?

02:53.246 --> 02:56.756
They knew you would
abandon them and run away

02:56.988 --> 02:59.315
as soon as you returned.
So they had to keep you here

02:59.435 --> 03:01.192
if not with a simple lie.

03:02.330 --> 03:03.763
You don't believe me.

