03:19.351 --> 03:20.581
Where are we?

03:21.515 --> 03:23.521
Far from the roots of Salem.

03:42.790 --> 03:44.161
Now do you believe me?

03:44.706 --> 03:47.283
You test my word with my very life.

03:47.305 --> 03:49.795
- Forgive me.
- I am bound to this hell.

03:49.915 --> 03:51.675
At present, this very house.

03:52.368 --> 03:54.234
But if you must go, then go.

03:54.258 --> 03:55.535
No.

03:56.528 --> 03:58.038
I will not leave you here.

03:58.278 --> 04:00.078
A promise easily made,

04:00.109 --> 04:02.499
yet we will see just how
loyal you prove to be.

04:02.518 --> 04:05.577
I worship you. Ask of me anything.

04:05.987 --> 04:08.280
There is only one way
we can be together.

04:08.917 --> 04:10.380
You must choose.

04:10.383 --> 04:12.604
Me or the boy.

04:13.120 --> 04:14.587
Will you help me kill him?

