05:08.993 --> 05:10.182
Anne?

05:11.265 --> 05:12.741
I'm here, my love.

05:12.808 --> 05:14.398
I got your message and came at once.

05:14.436 --> 05:16.980
- Are you not well?
- I have vomited twice this morning.

05:17.012 --> 05:19.296
- Ohh.
- Never felt so well.

05:20.896 --> 05:22.710
Then let the light in.

05:22.830 --> 05:25.144
The sun shines but a few more days.

05:25.207 --> 05:27.691
We must make the most of it.

05:31.438 --> 05:32.584
But...

05:46.776 --> 05:48.839
But it is hardly a week.

05:49.339 --> 05:50.752
I believe...

05:50.872 --> 05:54.957
my witch blood has quickened
the speed of life itself.

06:00.798 --> 06:02.345
My child...

06:04.210 --> 06:05.624
Our chance.

06:08.102 --> 06:10.035
Life is a force of nature

06:10.073 --> 06:12.234
that not even the
devil's fire can stifle.

06:15.688 --> 06:17.668
Here, amid all this turmoil...

06:19.273 --> 06:21.223
my dream comes true.

06:25.546 --> 06:27.266
I will be a loving father.

06:27.590 --> 06:30.913
And I will be the best
mother this baby could have.

06:32.274 --> 06:35.530
I implore you to come
to the Sibley house. Now.

06:35.901 --> 06:37.726
I must have you and...

06:38.537 --> 06:40.436
and our child safe.

06:42.351 --> 06:44.452
I must finish a few things.

06:45.022 --> 06:47.093
Then I will gather what I need

06:47.155 --> 06:50.496
and come by the end
of the day. I promise.

06:50.944 --> 06:53.393
Promise me you will come
as quickly as you can.

