07:15.402 --> 07:16.474
Hello?

07:17.573 --> 07:18.709
Who's there?

07:39.480 --> 07:41.276
I know what you are.

07:43.705 --> 07:46.631
I have no choice. I am
only doing what is best.

07:48.884 --> 07:50.711
Leave me alone!

